1. *Gola* istina je da ne mogu da se setim šta sam uradio prošle noći. (The naked truth is that I can't remember what I did last night.)
2. Ovo je *gola* laž! (This is a barefaced lie!)
3. Kada sam se okrenula, videla sam *golu* ženu kako trči ulicom. (When I turned around, I saw a naked woman running down the street.)
4. Moramo da se suočimo sa *golim* činjenicama. (We have to face the bare facts.)
5. Uzeo je *golu* žarulju i stavio je u fioku. (He took a naked light bulb and put it in the drawer.)
6. Nikada ne idem *gol* u bazen. (I never go naked in the pool.)
7. *Gole* planine pružaju nezaboravne pejzaže. (Bare mountains provide unforgettable landscapes.)
8. *Goli* zidovi su bili ukrašeni muralima. (Bare walls were adorned with murals.)
9. Osvojio je zlatnu medalju u *golim* rukama. (He won the gold medal with bare hands.)
10. *Golo* nebo se činilo beskrajno. (The bare sky seemed endless.)